N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5100.8 - Powers reserved

State Regulations

All powers not specifically defined in this Subchapter
are reserved to the commission under the laws creating the commission and
specifying the commission's powers and duties. Notes
